nt  Kempty Falls: Beautiful waterfall en route  Barkot: Base for Yamunotri, relax & acclimatize  Stay: Barkot'),(514,155,'Day 2: Barkot → Yamunotri → Barkot',NULL,NULL,'2025-03-22 22:21:52','2025-03-26 15:56:57','Distance: 40 km drive + 6 km trek (one way)  Route: Barkot → Janki Chatti → Yamunotri  Activities:  Drive to Janki Chatti  Trek to Yamunotri Temple (can hire pony/doli if needed)  Visit Surya Kund (Hot Water Spring) and Divya Shila  Return: Back to Barkot for overnight stay'),(515,155,'Day 3: Barkot → Uttarkashi',NULL,NULL,'2025-03-22 22:21:52','2025-03-26 15:56:57','Distance: ~100 km | Time: 4-5 hours  Route: Barkot → Dharasu → Uttarkashi  Places to Visit:  Prakateshwar Mahadev Cave Temple (en route)  In Uttarkashi:  Kashi Vishwanath Temple  Shakti Temple (Big Trishul)  Stay: Uttarkashi'),(516,155,'Day 4: Uttarkashi → Guptkashi',NULL,NULL,'2025-03-22 22:21:52','2025-03-26 15:56:57','Distance: ~200 km | Time: 8-9 hours  Route: Uttarkashi → Tehri Dam → Srinagar → Rudraprayag → Guptkashi  Highlights:  Scenic drive alongside Tehri Lake  Views of confluences (Sangams): Devprayag, Rudraprayag  Evening visit to Ardh Narishwar Temple, Guptkashi  Stay: Guptkashi'),(517,155,'Day 5: Guptkashi → Kedarnath (Trek)',NULL,NULL,'2025-03-22 22:21:52','2025-03-26 15:56:57','Distance: 30 km drive + 18 km trek  Route: Guptkashi → Sonprayag → Gaurikund → Kedarnath  Activities:  Early drive to Sonprayag & Gaurikund  Start 18 km trek to Kedarnath Temple  Visit the divine Kedarnath Temple  Stay: Kedarnath (basic lodges or GMVN camps)'),(518,155,'Day 6: Kedarnath → Guptkashi / Rudraprayag',NULL,NULL,'2025-03-22 22:21:52','2025-03-26 15:56:57','Trek back: Kedarnath → Gaurikund → Sonprayag  Drive to: Guptkashi or Rudraprayag (as per your comfort)  Relax & Rest'),(519,155,'Day 7: Guptkashi / Rudraprayag → Dehradun',NULL,NULL,'2025-03-22 22:21:52','2025-03-26 15:56:57','Distance: ~200-220 km | Time: 8-9 hours  Route: Guptkashi → Srinagar → Devprayag → Rishikesh → Dehradun  Optional Stops:  Devprayag (Alaknanda & Bhagirathi confluence)  Rishikesh Sightseeing: Laxman Jhula, Ram Jhula, Ganga Aarti (if time permits)'),(520,156,'Day 1: Haridwar → Barkot (approx. 200 km / 7-8 hrs)',NULL,NULL,'2025-03-22 22:21:52','2025-03-26 15:56:57','Morning: Depart from Haridwar after breakfast.  Enroute Sightseeing:  Mussoorie (optional, quick stop): Kempty Falls.  Lakhamandal Temple (mythologically significant site near Yamunotri route).  Evening: Reach Barkot. Rest and acclimatize.  Stay: Barkot.'),(521,156,'Day 2: Barkot → Yamunotri → Barkot (approx. 90 km drive + 12 km trek)',NULL,NULL,'2025-03-22 22:21:52','2025-03-26 15:56:57','Morning: Drive to Janki Chatti (base for Yamunotri trek).  Trek:  6 km one way trek to Yamunotri Temple (can hire pony/palki if needed).  Visit Surya Kund (hot water spring) and Divya Shila.  Afternoon: Return trek to Janki Chatti.  Evening: Back to Barkot.  Stay: Barkot.'),(522,156,'Day 3: Barkot → Uttarkashi (approx. 100 km / 4 hrs)',NULL,NULL,'2025-03-22 22:21:52','2025-03-26 15:56:57','Morning: Drive towards Uttarkashi.  Sightseeing in Uttarkashi:  Kashi Vishwanath Temple.  Shakti Temple (giant trishul).  Nehrukund & Maneri Dam (optional).  Stay: Uttarkashi'),(523,156,'Day 4: Uttarkashi → Guptkashi (approx. 230 km / 9-10 hrs)',NULL,NULL,'2025-03-22 22:21:52','2025-03-26 15:56:57','Early start due to long drive.  Beautiful views of Tehri Dam en route.  Evening arrival at Guptkashi.  Visit Ardh Narishwar Temple if time permits.  Stay: Guptkashi.'),(524,156,'Day 5: Guptkashi → Kedarnath (drive 30 km to Sonprayag + 18 km trek)',NULL,NULL,'2025-03-22 22:21:52','2025-03-26 15:56:57','Drive to Sonprayag & then transfer to Gaurikund (small vehicle allowed).  Trek 18 km to Kedarnath Temple (Pony/Palki/Helicopter options available).  Visit:  Kedarnath Temple darshan.  Bhairav Temple (optional short trek).  Overnight stay at Kedarnath (basic accommodation).'),(525,156,'Day 6: Kedarnath → Guptkashi (trek back & drive)',NULL,NULL,'2025-03-22 22:21:52','2025-03-26 15:56:57','Morning return trek to Gaurikund.  Drive back to Guptkashi.  Rest and relax after trek.  Stay: Guptkashi.'),(526,156,'Day 7: Guptkashi → Haridwar (approx. 210 km / 8 hrs)',NULL,NULL,'2025-03-22 22:21:52','2025-03-26 15:56:57','Drive back to Haridwar.  Optional stops at Rudraprayag (confluence of Alaknanda & Mandakini Rivers) and Devprayag (Alaknanda & Bhagirathi confluence forming Ganga).  Reach Haridwar by evening.'),(527,157,'Day 1: Rishikesh → Barkot (Approx. 170 km / 6-7 hrs)',NULL,NULL,'2025-03-22 22:21:52','2025-03-26 15:56:57','Morning: Depart from Rishikesh after breakfast.  Enroute places:  Devprayag (confluence of Alaknanda & Bhagirathi rivers)  Tehri Dam (optional stop)  Evening: Reach Barkot, check-in at hotel.  Overnight: Barkot'),(528,157,'Day 2: Barkot → Yamunotri → Barkot (36 km drive + 6 km trek one way)',NULL,NULL,'2025-03-22 22:21:52','2025-03-26 15:56:57','Morning: Drive to Janki Chatti (36 km), then trek 6 km to Yamunotri Temple.  Enroute highlights:  Surya Kund (hot water spring)  Divya Shila (sacred stone)  Darshan at Yamunotri Temple  Return trek to Janki Chatti → Drive back to Barkot.  Overnight: Barkot'),(529,157,'Day 3: Barkot → Uttarkashi (Approx. 100 km / 4 hrs)',NULL,NULL,'2025-03-22 22:21:52','2025-03-26 15:56:57','Visit Kashi Vishwanath Temple in Uttarkashi.  Stroll at Maneri Dam & Bhali Dam if time allows.  Explore local market.  Overnight: Uttarkashi'),(530,157,'Day 4: Uttarkashi → Guptkashi (Approx. 220 km / 8-9 hrs)',NULL,NULL,'2025-03-22 22:21:52','2025-03-26 15:56:57','Long scenic drive alongside rivers and through the mountains.  Enroute places:  Mandakini & Alaknanda river confluence at Rudraprayag.  Stop at Chopta (Mini Switzerland) if time permits.  Reach Guptkashi by evening.  Visit Ardh Narishwar Temple.  Overnight: Guptkashi'),(531,157,'Day 5: Guptkashi → Kedarnath (Drive 30 km + 18 km trek)',NULL,NULL,'2025-03-22 22:21:52','2025-03-26 15:56:57','Early morning drive to Sonprayag.  From Sonprayag, proceed to Gaurikund → Start 18 km trek to Kedarnath.  Reach Kedarnath, visit Kedarnath Temple, evening Aarti.  Overnight: Kedarnath (option to stay at GMVN camps/hotels).'),(532,157,'Day 6: Kedarnath → Guptkashi (18 km trek + drive)',NULL,NULL,'2025-03-22 22:21:52','2025-03-26 15:56:57','Morning Darshan (if missed).  Trek back to Gaurikund → Drive to Guptkashi.  Rest and relax after trek.  Overnight: Guptkashi'),(533,157,'Day 7: Guptkashi → Rishikesh (Approx. 210 km / 8 hrs)',NULL,NULL,'2025-03-22 22:21:52','2025-03-26 15:56:57','Drive back to Rishikesh.  Enroute sightseeing:  Rudraprayag Sangam  Devprayag (if skipped earlier)  Evening arrival in Rishikesh.  Optional: Visit Ganga Aarti at Triveni Ghat.');
